Hello!

1:04:33.034 --> 1:04:34.000
Hello?

1:04:48.103 --> 1:04:49.310
Is anyone there?

1:04:52.068 --> 1:04:53.310
I'm from next door.

1:05:06.068 --> 1:05:07.137
Hello?

1:07:11.793 --> 1:07:13.068
<i>Chloe?</i>

1:07:34.724 --> 1:07:37.379
<i>Sweetie, you gotta go
back to bed.</i>

1:08:10.724 --> 1:08:13.310
<i>Chloe, say happy Fourth of July.</i>

1:08:31.448 --> 1:08:33.862
<i>You've reached
the voicemail of Dr. Sophia Lynch</i>

1:08:33.862 --> 1:08:36.000
<i>with the Northeast Eye
and Ear Institute.</i>

1:08:36.000 --> 1:08:39.000
<i>Please leave a message and I will
return your call during office hours.</i>

1:08:39.000 --> 1:08:40.275
<i>Thank you.</i>

1:08:41.931 --> 1:08:45.758
Dr. Lynch, it's Chloe Grayden.

1:08:47.413 --> 1:08:48.724
I know it's late...

1:08:49.551 --> 1:08:50.551
or early even...

1:08:51.517 --> 1:08:53.965
<i>I'm so sorry to call you,</i>

1:08:53.965 --> 1:08:55.758
<i>I just,</i>

1:08:55.758 --> 1:08:58.620
<i>I think something's wrong
with the procedure.</i>

1:08:59.724 --> 1:09:02.482
<i>There's been some bleeding.</i>

1:09:04.620 --> 1:09:06.896
<i>I'm getting ringing in my ears</i>

1:09:08.310 --> 1:09:09.896
<i>and it's getting worse.</i>

1:09:12.793 --> 1:09:15.310
<i>I don't mean to bother you.
I just...</i>

1:09:15.310 --> 1:09:18.655
<i>I needed someone
to talk to about all of this.</i>

1:09:22.758 --> 1:09:24.655
<i>Please just call me
when you can.</i>

1:09:26.655 --> 1:09:27.689
<i>Bye.</i>

1:10:39.620 --> 1:10:40.724
Shit.

1:10:42.482 --> 1:10:43.379
Hello?

1:10:43.379 --> 1:10:45.034
<i>Hey, Chloe.</i>

1:10:45.034 --> 1:10:47.413
<i>Hank told me you came by
to use his power drill.</i>

1:10:47.413 --> 1:10:48.448
<i>Is everything okay?</i>

1:10:48.448 --> 1:10:50.000
Dad, yeah, yeah.

1:10:50.758 --> 1:10:51.827
I'm okay.

1:10:51.827 --> 1:10:53.482
<i>Now why would you
need a drill?</i>

1:11:03.413 --> 1:11:04.448
Hello?

1:11:05.793 --> 1:11:07.034
Dad, I can't hear you.

1:11:12.034 --> 1:11:13.793
<i>Now we talked about
this... you...</i>

1:11:13.793 --> 1:11:15.068
Please calm down, I'm fine.

1:11:21.586 --> 1:11:22.482
Dad?

1:11:27.724 --> 1:11:30.137
<i>Sweetie,
you gotta go back to bed.</i>

1:11:59.000 --> 1:12:00.034
<i>Chloe?</i>

1:12:01.172 --> 1:12:03.448
<i>Chloe, it's Dr. Sophia Lynch.</i>

1:12:09.586 --> 1:12:11.724
Your ears look fine.

1:12:15.655 --> 1:12:18.689
You know, you are the first one
to show positive results.

1:12:20.724 --> 1:12:22.000
- Really?
- Mm-hmm.

1:12:23.758 --> 1:12:24.793
Am I the only one?

1:12:24.793 --> 1:12:27.517
So far, but, it's early.

1:12:28.965 --> 1:12:31.517
You are our star subject, though.

1:12:36.586 --> 1:12:37.827
It was working, like...

1:12:39.068 --> 1:12:40.068
really well.

1:12:43.068 --> 1:12:44.034
But I'm...

1:12:45.068 --> 1:12:46.620
hearing things.

1:12:47.724 --> 1:12:49.517
That's good, right? I mean,

1:12:50.620 --> 1:12:52.103
that's what's
supposed to happen.

1:12:55.000 --> 1:12:58.172
No, like... like things
that aren't there.

1:12:59.758 --> 1:13:01.482
Yeah, no people who have
regained some...

1:13:02.793 --> 1:13:05.413
some hearing through
cochlear implants

1:13:06.206 --> 1:13:08.655
they're often known to have

1:13:08.655 --> 1:13:09.862
auditory hallucinations.

1:13:11.310 --> 1:13:14.103
It can be hard to distinguish between
what's real and what's imagined.

1:13:15.275 --> 1:13:17.896
It could just be symptoms
of sensory overload.

1:13:18.862 --> 1:13:20.517
Sustained loud noises can,

1:13:21.517 --> 1:13:22.862
they can sound like voices.

1:13:27.034 --> 1:13:32.172
Chloe, this is a lot for
anyone to handle.

1:13:34.655 --> 1:13:37.586
It could be helpful to
talk through it.

1:13:41.620 --> 1:13:44.655
Have you reached out to any
of the therapists we
recommended?

1:13:48.793 --> 1:13:49.793
No.

1:13:51.034 --> 1:13:53.000
I'm sorry, I know it's my fault.

1:13:53.896 --> 1:13:55.000
No, no, it's...

1:13:55.689 --> 1:13:56.655
hey.

1:13:57.724 --> 1:14:00.896
How about you go get dressed

1:14:00.896 --> 1:14:02.689
and we get dinner?

1:14:05.310 --> 1:14:07.103
Yeah?

1:14:07.103 --> 1:14:09.965
- Yeah.
- Let's get away from this place
for a bit.

1:14:13.137 --> 1:14:14.862
Yeah, yeah, I'd like that.

1:14:19.206 --> 1:14:22.965
I'm realizing I only
really know you from your file.

1:14:24.068 --> 1:14:24.827
What are you up to?

1:14:25.793 --> 1:14:27.206
Are you in school, or...?

1:14:28.862 --> 1:14:29.379
Kinda.

1:14:30.275 --> 1:14:31.172
I took the semester off.

1:14:31.965 --> 1:14:33.827
For your project, actually

1:14:33.827 --> 1:14:35.068
and to help my dad
sell the house.

1:14:36.068 --> 1:14:37.275
Is it just the two of you?

1:14:38.620 --> 1:14:39.241
Yeah,

1:14:40.068 --> 1:14:42.034
my mom left when I was eight.

1:14:43.275 --> 1:14:44.551
Disappeared.

1:14:45.275 --> 1:14:47.034
We don't know, actually.

1:14:49.655 --> 1:14:51.655
I was the last
person to see her.

1:14:53.896 --> 1:14:54.862
I mean I was in this...

1:14:56.206 --> 1:14:59.758
coma for six months from
the meningitis.

1:15:01.000 --> 1:15:02.551
And I came out of it and I

1:15:03.344 --> 1:15:06.241
lost my hearing and my mom.

1:15:07.931 --> 1:15:10.620
Then got set back at
school and...

1:15:12.310 --> 1:15:17.655
just like this black
hole it's like...

1:15:19.862 --> 1:15:21.724
just, an invisible weight.

1:15:24.689 --> 1:15:25.793
But,

1:15:26.827 --> 1:15:27.931
it is what it is, right?

1:15:29.620 --> 1:15:32.172
Forces just beyond my control.

1:15:37.379 --> 1:15:39.000
You know I was thinking,

1:15:40.413 --> 1:15:42.275
maybe after this,

1:15:42.275 --> 1:15:43.689
I could like become a counselor

1:15:45.068 --> 1:15:47.310
or something for people
who have the procedure.

1:15:48.758 --> 1:15:52.620
We really have quite a
ways off from that.

1:15:54.034 --> 1:15:56.655
We have the trials,
we have to get approvals...

1:15:56.655 --> 1:15:57.931
- Yeah, no I...
- First...

1:15:57.931 --> 1:15:59.275
No, it's...

1:16:00.689 --> 1:16:01.793
I see.

1:16:03.896 --> 1:16:06.655
Maybe, yeah. Maybe
down the road.

1:16:07.689 --> 1:16:08.862
- Yeah.
- It could be helpful.

1:16:12.034 --> 1:16:13.034
Thank you.

1:16:25.034 --> 1:16:26.310
It sounds like
television static.

1:16:35.000 --> 1:16:40.793
You know, I still see album covers
and I see singers, what if the way

1:16:40.793 --> 1:16:43.379
that I imagine their songs is
better than
the way that they actually are, right?

1:16:44.758 --> 1:16:47.206
Oh, no I... I don't
keep up with music

1:16:47.206 --> 1:16:48.965
or trends or anything like that,
I just...

1:16:49.896 --> 1:16:51.862
you know, whatever's on.

1:16:51.862 --> 1:16:52.896
Yeah.

1:16:53.965 --> 1:16:55.034
Yeah, I remember like...

1:16:56.068 --> 1:16:58.000
bits of songs, like fragments.

1:16:58.965 --> 1:17:00.793
In my dreams, usually.

1:17:02.344 --> 1:17:04.724
I mean, I could always
hear my mom though.

1:17:06.448 --> 1:17:10.241
It's like she was the only clear voice
in my head the whole time.

1:17:12.000 --> 1:17:13.000
It's actually... that's...

1:17:13.379 --> 1:17:15.965
that's why I reached out to you
and your project.

1:17:17.896 --> 1:17:21.896
I was never ashamed
of my deafness but I felt like...

1:17:23.310 --> 1:17:26.413
if the volume of the world
got turned back up again

1:17:27.862 --> 1:17:29.241
I wouldn't hear her anymore.

1:17:29.241 --> 1:17:30.310
Like...

1:17:31.379 --> 1:17:32.862
she'd stop calling me back here.

1:17:33.344 --> 1:17:34.379
Hmm...

1:17:38.068 --> 1:17:39.931
Do you still hear her?

1:17:41.172 --> 1:17:42.172
Of course not.

1:17:43.310 --> 1:17:45.000
Your process worked, didn't it?

1:17:50.103 --> 1:17:51.827
Maybe we should get the check.

1:17:52.862 --> 1:17:54.000
Just a minute, hold on.

1:17:56.413 --> 1:17:57.482
Do you know this?

1:18:01.896 --> 1:18:03.931
- No... no I don't.
- I love it.

1:18:18.172 --> 1:18:21.000
<i>♪ The sun and sea are smiling</i>

1:18:22.517 --> 1:18:25.000
<i>♪ When you're going to bed</i>

1:18:26.896 --> 1:18:30.000
<i>♪ I wish Allah would will me</i>

1:18:31.310 --> 1:18:34.137
<i>♪ A piece of iron in my head</i>

1:18:36.034 --> 1:18:38.793
<i>♪ On my knees and wishing</i>

1:18:40.896 --> 1:18:45.206
<i>♪ On my knees and
breaking hands ♪</i>

1:19:03.206 --> 1:19:06.379
I can't get over
how bright the stars are outside
the city.

1:19:06.379 --> 1:19:07.413
Yeah.

1:19:10.137 --> 1:19:11.551
I wonder what they sound like.

1:19:28.931 --> 1:19:31.206
Sorry, it's gotten
a little out of control.

1:19:32.517 --> 1:19:36.000
Oh, it's okay...
there's always tomorrow...

1:19:36.000 --> 1:19:37.034
fresh start.

1:19:43.379 --> 1:19:45.931
It's... getting late.

1:19:47.000 --> 1:19:47.517
Yeah.

1:19:48.172 --> 1:19:50.206
You could stay if you want.

1:19:53.344 --> 1:19:57.034
I mean you could sleep
on the couch or not.

1:19:57.931 --> 1:20:01.275
Oh, Chloe, I...

1:20:05.896 --> 1:20:06.827
Don't go.

1:20:11.206 --> 1:20:13.034
I... I
really should...

1:20:14.103 --> 1:20:15.413
I'm sorry.

1:20:18.379 --> 1:20:20.965
You know, there's
something else I need to say.

1:20:24.206 --> 1:20:25.068
You weren't totally
honest with me.

1:20:27.068 --> 1:20:31.103
When your results were so positive,
I followed up on you. I had to.

1:20:32.448 --> 1:20:34.310
What do you mean?

1:20:34.310 --> 1:20:36.931
You should've told me
you were taking antidepressants.

1:20:36.931 --> 1:20:38.206
It could corrupt the study.

1:20:39.448 --> 1:20:42.517
And your mental state with
your mom and...

1:20:42.517 --> 1:20:45.344
that can make everything
so much harder than it already is.

1:20:48.689 --> 1:20:52.172
I don't see how that
matters right now.

1:20:52.172 --> 1:20:55.000
Of course it matters.
It all matters.

1:20:55.000 --> 1:20:57.931
I have to protect the project.

1:20:57.931 --> 1:21:00.034
You should've been honest with me.

1:21:01.310 --> 1:21:06.275
You are the first person
in the history of human kind

1:21:06.275 --> 1:21:13.344
to have regained your hearing
like this...

1:21:16.103 --> 1:21:17.931
Shoot. Okay, hold on, I'm sorry.

1:21:17.931 --> 1:21:21.413
I'm sorry, I...
I didn't mean to upset you, I just...

1:21:21.413 --> 1:21:22.344
No, no, I get it, I should...

1:21:23.586 --> 1:21:25.586
I should've told you
about my prescription.

1:21:26.379 --> 1:21:27.689
Oh, my god.

1:21:27.689 --> 1:21:29.344
Sorry, I'm just...

1:21:36.413 --> 1:21:38.206
I think I'm going to puke,
I'm sorry.

1:22:07.206 --> 1:22:08.275
Chloe?

1:22:09.137 --> 1:22:10.137
<i>Come in.</i>

1:22:16.586 --> 1:22:18.379
They just won't stop ringing.

1:22:26.241 --> 1:22:27.724
I really messed this up,
didn't I?

1:22:59.586 --> 1:23:00.724
Shit.

1:23:26.448 --> 1:23:27.655
Dr. Lynch?

1:26:03.827 --> 1:26:04.827
Joshua?

1:26:18.689 --> 1:26:19.793
Joshua?

1:27:39.517 --> 1:27:40.758
Saw your car.

1:27:43.655 --> 1:27:44.310
What is all this?

1:27:45.068 --> 1:27:47.034
I knew it, you can hear.

1:27:49.344 --> 1:27:51.448
- It's not like that.
- Have you been faking?

1:27:53.448 --> 1:27:54.551
You've been watching me.

1:27:55.517 --> 1:27:56.862
You're the one next door.

1:27:56.862 --> 1:27:58.551
We take care of that house.

1:27:59.689 --> 1:28:01.517
I heard you throwing a party.

1:28:02.758 --> 1:28:04.448
- You kept me up all night.
- Wait, what?

1:28:04.448 --> 1:28:06.689
- I heard you, okay?
- Wait, what are you talking about,

1:28:06.689 --> 1:28:07.586
you heard a party?

1:28:08.896 --> 1:28:10.586
No one's been over there
except for me.

1:28:14.068 --> 1:28:16.827
Okay. I'm not stupid,
I'm not crazy,

1:28:16.827 --> 1:28:18.413
stop this shit!

1:28:18.413 --> 1:28:19.482
Wait.

1:28:22.620 --> 1:28:23.931
I saw something

1:28:25.586 --> 1:28:26.586
at your dad's
cottage months ago.

1:28:28.655 --> 1:28:31.482
That's why I've been watching it,
to try to figure out what's
there.

1:28:32.862 --> 1:28:34.862
I mean I thought I was
seeing things,

1:28:34.862 --> 1:28:37.034
hearing things and then
you showed up.

1:28:40.965 --> 1:28:42.379
They're vibrations. Frequencies.

1:28:43.965 --> 1:28:47.068
All around us, magnetic fields,
things that we can't see or hear.

1:28:50.655 --> 1:28:51.586
But you can.

1:28:57.551 --> 1:28:59.000
It's a spirit world.

1:29:16.448 --> 1:29:17.758
This is an ultrasound.

1:29:19.551 --> 1:29:22.379
It's been adjusted to pick up
frequencies beyond our senses.

1:29:23.000 --> 1:29:24.034
Listen.

1:29:26.448 --> 1:29:27.793
What are you hearing right now?

1:29:29.862 --> 1:29:31.103
Nothing.

1:29:32.827 --> 1:29:34.379
Why did you come back here?

1:29:39.172 --> 1:29:40.896
<i>Chloe?</i>

1:29:45.034 --> 1:29:47.482
It wasn't a choice.
Something called you here...

1:29:48.827 --> 1:29:50.586
- Your mother.
- Stop it.

1:29:50.586 --> 1:29:52.034
Wait, listen!

1:30:05.551 --> 1:30:06.793
Stop it! Stop!

1:30:06.793 --> 1:30:08.482
- Wait!
- Stop it! Stop!

1:30:08.482 --> 1:30:10.551
- Stop! Stop! It's just fucking
noise!
- Wait, just...

1:30:10.551 --> 1:30:13.068
If I see you over at my house again
I'm calling the police.

1:30:13.068 --> 1:30:14.068
Don't be like this.

1:30:15.103 --> 1:30:16.724
Can't you see? Don't fight it!

1:30:16.724 --> 1:30:18.517
You stay away from me.

1:30:19.172 --> 1:30:21.758
Stay away from my house, please.

1:31:07.551 --> 1:31:09.931
<i>You've reached
the voice mail of Dr. Sophia Lynch</i>

1:31:09.931 --> 1:31:12.034
<i>with the Northeast Eye
and Ear Institute.</i>

1:31:12.034 --> 1:31:15.137
<i>Please leave a message and I
will return your call during
office hours.</i>

1:31:15.137 --> 1:31:16.068
<i>Thank you!</i>

1:31:19.068 --> 1:31:20.517
Hi, Dr. Lynch?

1:31:21.275 --> 1:31:23.000
Sophia, sorry.

1:31:24.620 --> 1:31:25.689
It's Chloe.

1:31:28.275 --> 1:31:31.206
What happened to you?
I mean, I woke up and you were gone.

1:31:35.000 --> 1:31:36.620
I know I screwed things up...

1:31:38.965 --> 1:31:40.551
I just want to talk it through.

1:31:43.793 --> 1:31:44.827
Make it better.

1:31:47.310 --> 1:31:48.241
Please call me.

1:33:41.379 --> 1:33:42.620
<i>Chloe?</i>

1:33:44.793 --> 1:33:45.724
Mom?

1:33:50.275 --> 1:33:51.724
<i>Chloe, is that you?</i>

1:34:10.068 --> 1:34:11.275
<i>I can see you.</i>

1:34:19.034 --> 1:34:20.000
<i>My god,</i>

1:34:22.758 --> 1:34:24.172
<i>how did you get so big?</i>

1:36:06.965 --> 1:36:08.413
Can you hear me okay?

1:36:11.172 --> 1:36:12.344
Good.

1:36:12.344 --> 1:36:13.896
That's good.

1:36:15.896 --> 1:36:16.896
Your dad...

1:36:18.241 --> 1:36:19.965
he called me, he was concerned
when you didn't pick up your phone.

1:36:21.862 --> 1:36:25.103
With the storm,
he wanted me to come check on you.

1:36:30.241 --> 1:36:31.344
And with good cause.

1:36:35.275 --> 1:36:36.896
You were...

1:36:38.586 --> 1:36:40.172
laying on the floor.

1:36:41.413 --> 1:36:42.827
Your ears were bleeding.

1:36:46.103 --> 1:36:46.931
We should call Dr. Lynch.

