1:37:01.620 --> 1:37:02.862
I've got a generator.

1:37:04.965 --> 1:37:05.965
I'll go get it going.

1:37:08.000 --> 1:37:08.896
Hey,

1:37:12.103 --> 1:37:13.344
you can relax now.

1:37:15.482 --> 1:37:16.586
Have some tea.

1:37:18.517 --> 1:37:20.448
Storm's going to pass
in the morning.

1:37:26.068 --> 1:37:27.206
It's going to be okay.

1:37:29.379 --> 1:37:30.482
I just know it.

1:37:35.206 --> 1:37:36.137
Okay.

1:37:37.275 --> 1:37:38.206
Okay.

1:37:39.482 --> 1:37:40.517
Thank you.

1:40:15.689 --> 1:40:16.724
You're standing!

1:40:18.206 --> 1:40:19.379
That's good.

1:40:22.586 --> 1:40:23.551
Yeah...

1:40:25.310 --> 1:40:27.034
I feel kind of dizzy.

1:40:27.034 --> 1:40:28.172
Come sit down.

1:40:40.724 --> 1:40:41.724
Your feet cold?

1:40:43.793 --> 1:40:46.793
I'm feeling like the chills.

1:40:50.724 --> 1:40:51.758
You're safe here.

1:40:54.068 --> 1:40:55.206
You can relax now.

1:40:59.655 --> 1:41:01.068
I'm going to take care of you.

1:41:09.689 --> 1:41:10.793
Where's your bathroom?

1:41:14.206 --> 1:41:15.241
It's over here.

1:41:49.517 --> 1:41:52.448
You okay in there?

1:41:53.758 --> 1:41:55.551
Yeah...

1:41:55.551 --> 1:41:59.655
just feeling really sick.
Please give me a few minutes.

1:42:03.620 --> 1:42:05.758
That tea's going to make
it all better.

1:42:13.172 --> 1:42:14.172
All better.

1:42:17.413 --> 1:42:18.517
What was that?

1:42:19.344 --> 1:42:20.379
Nothing.

1:42:21.620 --> 1:42:22.724
Dropped something.

1:42:34.413 --> 1:42:35.413
You okay in there?

1:42:37.344 --> 1:42:38.413
No, just... just...

1:42:39.241 --> 1:42:40.275
give me a minute.

1:42:57.482 --> 1:42:58.586
I can hear them.

1:43:06.275 --> 1:43:07.379
Hear what they're saying.

1:43:11.379 --> 1:43:12.379
Do you hear them?

1:43:22.896 --> 1:43:24.241
I hear them.

1:43:29.344 --> 1:43:30.827
The ones I took care of.

1:43:49.413 --> 1:43:50.517
Chloe, you hear me?

1:44:09.482 --> 1:44:11.206
Chloe, what are you
doing in there?

1:44:14.379 --> 1:44:16.896
Open the goddamn door, sweetheart.

1:44:28.379 --> 1:44:29.689
Chloe!

1:44:35.068 --> 1:44:36.275
Chloe!

